@Ivans_translator Hi Iváns! I'm not originally from Galicia, so I normally use the RAG for some terms. "Eixe" is a more correct term according to this:
https://academia.gal/dicionario/-/termo/busca/eixo

However, if you still think it would be better to have it as "eixo", please tell me.
